<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wǒ xū yào nǐ de huà yǔ, hǎo xiàng xū yào yǐn shí yī yàng.
 rú guǒ méi yǒu nǐ de huà yǔ, wǒ jiù méi yǒu lì liàng.
 zhǔ a wǒ xū yào nǐ de tóng zài, hǎo xiàng xū yào hū xī yī yàng.
 rú guǒ yǒu le nǐ de tóng zài, wǒ jiù miǎn le sǐ wáng.
 wǒ yào yī kào wǒ yào yī kào yé hé huá,
 jiù hǎo xiàng nà yī kē shù zāi zài shēng mìng de hé shuǐ páng.
 yán rè lái dào ya bù jù pà, gàn hàn zhī nián háo wú guà lǜ,
 yè zi qīng cuì jié guǒ bù zhǐ, wǒ yào yī kào yé hé huá.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a wǒ xū yào nǐ de huà 迦南308</title>
<hymn_number>308</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>